    "headline": "CenterPoint Energy Declares Regular Common Stock Dividend of $0.2400",
    "summary": "CenterPoint Energy, Inc.'s (NYSE: CNP) Board of Directors yesterday declared a regular quarterly cash dividend of $0.2400 per share on the issued and outstanding shares of Common Stock payable on September 10, 2026, to shareholders of record at the close of business on August 20, 2026. This represents a $0.0100 increase over the April 2026 declared dividend per share and in line with CenterPoint's targeted annual dividend per share growth rate of 6%.",
